Command Line Usage 
==================

To Build run the command

	sh build.sh

To call Java method from command line use
java defined_function -s sourcefilename -i sourcelanguage -t targetlanguage

Usage: javac defined_function [-options]       
	where options include:
	-s Source File name
	-i Source Language 
	-t Target Language

Example : java defined_function -s samples/messages.properties -i english -t hindi


Errors Handled
==================


1.) Source file doesn't exist.


2.) Invalid Source language.


3.) Invalid Target Language.


4.) Invalid number of arguments.


Features
==================

1.) Display Progress for the user.


